Linux fetch tool to get the system requirements for a game from steam

Usage:
    steamfetch [GAME TITLE]

Example (fetch Team Fortress 2):
    steamfetch tf2

Dependencies:
    coreutils (GNU)
    sed (GNU)
    awk (GNU)
    curl
    figlet (optional but recommended for large title)
